# NOTICE — Attributions and Sources

The `staff-engineer-mode` skill distills principles from canonical software engineering literature. The skill itself is original work; it cites and references the books below but does not reproduce copyrighted text beyond fair-use quotation. Each principle in `SKILL.md` is attributed to its source.

The reference files in `references/` contain short quotations attributed to their original authors and link to authoritative sources. All quotations are used under fair-use principles for commentary, criticism, and educational purposes.

