## Independent concepts cited

- **Hyrum's Law** — Hyrum Wright. <https://www.hyrumslaw.com/>
- **Chesterton's Fence** — G.K. Chesterton, *The Thing* (1929).
- **Two Hats / Make the change easy, then make the easy change** — Kent Beck, attributed via Fowler's *Refactoring*.
- **Postel's Robustness Principle** — Jon Postel, RFC 760 / RFC 1122.

## How to cite this skill

If you draw from this skill in your own work, attribution is appreciated but not required:

> staff-engineer-mode skill (2026). MIT License.

Always cite the underlying books when you use a principle from them — they did the original work.
